## Company [/api/company/{company_id}]

A Company object has the following attributes:

+ id
+ symbol
+ name
+ exchange
+ location
+ currency
+ open_price
+ previous_price
+ percent_change
+ year_high
+ ask_price
+ eps
+ peg
+ days_range
+ percent_change_fifty
+ percent_change_twohundred
+ volume
+ avg_volume
+ market_cap


+ Parameters
    + company_id: 1 (required, number) - Name of the Company in form of a number (1-1650)

