## Group Locations

Resources related to location in the API.

## Location [/api/location/{location_id}]

A Location object has the following attributes:

+ id
+ name
+ iso
+ capital
+ GDP
+ currency
+ exchange

+ Parameters
    + location_id: 1 (required, number) - Name of the Location in form of a number (1-11)

